data.title: Royal Netherlands Air Force (Koninklijke Luchtmacht) (Military Unit)
data.meta_description: Learn everything there is to know about Royal Netherlands Air Force (Koninklijke Luchtmacht) (Military Unit) at the hobbyDB database
data.text:
The Koninklijke Luchtmacht is 1 of 4 Dutch military units. The other 3 units are the Koninklijke Landmacht (Royal Army), the Koninklijke Marine (Royal Navy) and the Koninklijke Marechaussee (Military Police). The airforce became an independent military unit on March 11, 1953 and was entitled to call itself "Royal".
